- generalization of OS shell jobs. Alternatively, generalized unix init mechanism, which no child process cannot outlive.
- system administration function for monitoring process group
- ACID transaction orchestrator
- embedded in-memory database to serve shared serializable memory needs
- precursor to log-based message broker, i.e. design pattern for variable number of producers but fixed number of consumers, where all the consumers reside in a single process - this is to enable building a small-scale deferred request processing system
